OL,7,FA man who piloted an "unseaworthy"
OL,8,Fboat where four passengers drowned in
OL,9,Fthe English Channel has been found
OL,10,Fguilty of manslaughter.
OL,12,FIbrahima Bah, from Senegal and over
OL,13,F18, was charged with four counts of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter and one count of piloting
OL,15,Fto facilitate illegal entry into the
OL,16,FUK from France on 14 December 2022.
