OL,7,FA multi-agency search and rescue
OL,8,Foperation was launched off the Kent
OL,9,Fcoast, involving the Royal Navy,
OL,10,FFrench Navy, Coastguard, RNLI
OL,11,Flifeboats, ambulance service and
OL,12,Fpolice after the boat got into
OL,13,Fdifficulty.
OL,15,FDuring the operation, 39 people were
OL,16,Fbrought to shore in the port of Dover,
OL,17,Fbut four other people were pronounced
OL,18,Fdead.
