OL,3,CMan found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cmigrants who drowned in Channel
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FDuring the trial, jurors were told the
OL,8,Fhome-built, low-quality inflatable
OL,9,Fshould have had no more than 20 people
OL,10,Fon board but, in fact, tried to carry
OL,11,Fat least 43 people across the English
OL,12,FChannel that night.
OL,14,FWhile the majority of travellers paid
OL,15,Fthousands of euros to smugglers for a
OL,16,Fspot in the overcrowded vessel,
OL,17,Fprosecutor Duncan Atkinson KC said it
OL,18,Fappears Bah did not pay for his
OL,19,Fjourney because he piloted the dingy,
OL,20,Ftherefore owing his fellow passengers
OL,21,Fa "duty of care".
