OL,4,Cmigrants who drowned in Channel
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FThe court heard that it was Bah's
OL,8,Fdream to come to the UK to claim
OL,9,Fasylum, and he had left Senegal in
OL,10,F2019.
OL,12,FHe told police, when he arrived in the
OL,13,FUK, that he had travelled from Senegal
OL,14,Fto Mali, Algeria and then Libya,
OL,15,Fbefore going by boat to Italy using
OL,16,Fsmugglers.
