OL,4,Cmigrants who drowned in Channel
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FHe had previously worked on fishing
OL,8,Fboats in Senegal, sometimes helping
OL,9,Fwith fishing and steering the boat,
OL,10,Fand assisted in piloting the boat from
OL,11,FLibya to Italy.
OL,13,FLibby Clark, from the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service, said: "Bah
OL,15,Fclaimed that he had sailed boats
OL,16,Fbefore and, as a result, received free
OL,17,Fpassage, whereas everyone else on the
OL,18,Fboat had paid thousands of euros to
OL,19,Fmake the tragic journey.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
