OL,3,CMan found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cmigrants who drowned in Channel
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,F"The boat he piloted was never
OL,8,Fdesigned to undertake a crossing in
OL,9,Fthe world's busiest shipping lane and
OL,10,Fwould have been all but invisible to
OL,11,Fother ships.
OL,13,F"Navigation was carried out with just
OL,14,Fmobile phones as there were no other
OL,15,Fnavigational aids available.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
