OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F417A1708399603
OL,3,CMan found guilty over deaths of
OL,4,Cmigrants who drowned in Channel
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,F"There is no evidence to suggest that
OL,8,FBah had any training in piloting a
OL,9,Fboat like this or keeping people safe
OL,10,Fand, as the pilot, he assumed
OL,11,Fresponsibility for ensuring the safety
OL,12,Fof his fellow passengers.
OL,14,F"Any reasonable person would have
OL,15,Frecognised that by piloting such an
OL,16,Fill-equipped and overloaded boat in
OL,17,Fsuch dangerous circumstances, there
OL,18,Fwas an obvious risk of serious harm to
OL,19,Fthe passengers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
