OL,7,F"As a result of Bah's actions, four
OL,8,Fmen tragically lost their lives in the
OL,9,FChannel that night. Our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with their families."
OL,12,FBah will be sentenced at Canterbury
OL,13,FCrown Court on Friday February 23.
